Key Features Explained


1. Custom Hangman Drawing
The HangmanDrawingPanel inner class uses Graphics2D for smooth, anti-aliased rendering:

Gallows (brown wooden structure) is always visible
Body parts appear progressively (head → body → arms → legs)
Face expressions change based on game state (smile vs. X eyes)
2. Color-Coded Feedback
    Unguessed letters: Blue accent color
    Correct guesses: Green background
    Incorrect guesses: Red background
    Low lives warning: Attempts label turns red/yellow
3. Responsive Button States
   Buttons have hover effects (brighten on mouse-over)
   Disabled after being clicked
   Color changes immediately on guess
